## Prime Capital Bank

A banking system developed in C# using .NET, created to practice programming logic, data structures, and fundamental software developmente concepts.

This project is part of my portfolio and will be gradually expanded with new features, simulating functionalities commonly found in real-word banking systems.

## Current Features
- Bank account creation.
- Login.
- Deposit.
- Withdrawal.
- Money transfer between accounts.
- Interactive console menu.
- User input validation.

## Upcoming Features
- Login using account number and password.
- Restrict operations to authenticated users.
- Password change functionality.
- Login attempt validation.
- Investiment Area (Financial investmente simulation, investment return calculation, invested assests overview and investment withdrawal).
- Income Tax Calculator (Monthly income registration, annual average salary calculation, income tax based estimation based on the current tax brackets and income and tax reporting).

## Technologies
- C#
- .NET
- SQL Server
- Console Application
- Github

